                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-227-victim1278 t18280410-227-viclabel1213"></join>. On the 20th of March, I saw the prisoner in the shop; he was a stranger - I went and asked what he wanted; he said he came for relief - I saw the glass-case in confusion, and detained him; he then took three combs from his pocket - the officer came and took him.</p>
